ormal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c98b273597d7ac277454675ab84ceb7cf7780a","tid":352880,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點check到有</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴定絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲 一開始既時候 真係嚇撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁細個開始玩唔用套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw絲打加油，祝你早日康復"},{"pid":"c0643f7dc1323b3290f49a1e126bd6c1f11bb21a","tid":352880,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:26:16.000Z","msg":"輕鬆啦冇事嘅"},{"pid":"ce572384acac8adaef404131b835454a688ae795","tid":352880,"uid":14012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>抑鬱藥食咗年幾 7月頭終於停藥 點知停咗一個月就發現有腦瘤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">應該咩都可以答 反正好難自爆到</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">絲</span>打我都有腦瘤但係細你一歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左半邊身冇咩力 行路又行唔穩<br />\n我依家淨係希望過得幾耐得幾耐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日揩到個掣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實講未到巴打咁嚴重 我其實都係前日照 琴日出report 但係加埋有少少復發抑鬱 成個人心理好唔平衡 <br />\n巴打 你要加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e2da78510db71e8a41b909c1b146f7eb81b730","tid":352880,"uid":14012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇事就冇事 我都有由5歲開始就有 成日都覺得就死 今年生埋日就21  3年前開始就當佢唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我真係寧願死 呢兩日個人又頹到落谷底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 都要加油喔</blockquote><br />\n腦呢家野好神奇 影響d咩都有可能 你唔怕其實冇事 睇運唔中視力 行動能力 思考正常 頭痛當傷風感冒 一個負碌極慢or停止生長 多d搵野玩 記住自己只係為快樂生存 咁會好好多</blockquote><br />\n其實好灰 呢個禮拜頭痛得好緊要 <br />\n本身今朝飛菲律賓去潛水 點知最後去唔到 <br />\n點解 點解要係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你又唔諗下點解你有個腦瘤仲生存到係一個奇蹟，可能你人生有個任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗯...或者你岩既 有啲野唔經歷到唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">放下負</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">可以有咩任務 <br />\n反正人到最後都死 點解唔早啲死 自問自己既存在係浪費緊地球資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"8aa3bec16be7cb6dd5f636d8cc131c4341ea8529","tid":352880,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"臭西"},{"pid":"58f6356dbd9afb47cfdef7c9bc1fc43043eeeca7","tid":352880,"uid":79238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n有病未必係壞事 有機會思考反思 自己真正想過嘅生活<br />\n我都係18歲個年有咗個好罕有嘅病 好唔返但可以控制<br />\n做完手術覺得無痛無病發嘅一日已經好幸福開心<br />\nnormal day is good day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bc538d5b3e939ced9677f043c2ee9de883c547","tid":352880,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇事就冇事 我都有由5歲開始就有 成日都覺得就死 今年生埋日就21  3年前開始就當佢唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>