sg":"唔好諗咁多<br />\n襯仲有命 如果有錢就去下旅行<br />\n好好享受餘生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbc8888b4b61784639a8cc2f278db6e21d9fb80","tid":352880,"uid":7422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"抑鬱個段時間捱過左未？有曾經諗過自殺嗎？加油 希望你可以捱過呢個病 享受屬於你自己生命中嘅美好"},{"pid":"9ec5855a989fee25edf2fb9666f1258e067d5b72","tid":352880,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0c05384ed0526fda710d26e826b5d9a60502c7b","tid":352880,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T17:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 逼自己諗嘢正面啲會唔會對病情有幫助"},{"pid":"1c15e9ae13273289c596d72ad06903adbfc67bc5","tid":352880,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"有無考慮過攞d人奶放上網賣？<br />\n包你發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4026a0685f1c9ff090aaf2ca45a85d029ea4d16b","tid":352880,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"Pituitary adenoma <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b039e7bff39bdab08f3ed2df436ceea3a3ddad2","tid":352880,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T18:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pituitary adenoma <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thebraintumourcharity.org/understanding-brain-tumours/living-with-a-brain-tumour/side-effects/depression-and-brain-tumours/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebraintumourcharity.org%2Funderstanding-brain-tumours%2Fliving-with-a-brain-tumour%2Fside-effects%2Fdepression-and-brain-tumours%2F&h=8829e68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長期抑鬱係咪會導致腦瘤<img src