70,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得係因為有腦瘤所以有抑鬱"},{"pid":"f00dc8392a7e61f9672382fc81749a908c3b7482","tid":352880,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"抑鬱一年好小事啫"},{"pid":"311c7b2f20a431f827edfe45ac1b522480eea880","tid":352880,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"唔係想恐嚇你，識人有腦癌，一年內由發現去到死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩想做就做埋佢，好好諗一下自己有咩一定要做"},{"pid":"a5ada14b34b62fe37fd5522db56fac04bb25d4c8","tid":352880,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"無意冒犯 但講真你知道有腦瘤係咪開心過一吓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主支持你"},{"pid":"ad2e49f9f71b33a242f636d556bde346a4356b46","tid":352880,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:33:42.000Z","msg":"割咗佢啦<br />\nGod bless you"},{"pid":"31346838e8af664269e5d36447347eaa0817f5ac","tid":352880,"uid":44225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"加油呀"},{"pid":"dc48ee83bc6fc3f5e6bf37761812893cd05d333c","tid":352880,"uid":4412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係想恐嚇你，識人有腦癌，一年內由發現去到死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩想做就做埋佢，好好諗一下自己有咩一定要做</blockquote><br />\n癌同瘤係兩樣野<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"7f35455e2688d26243631609eb94440bf697486a","tid":352880,"uid":14012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 逼自己諗嘢正面啲會唔會對病情有幫助</blockquote> <br />\n<br />\n都要迫到先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經好努力架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2723f96a9ec67abdb65fbd27c241ef42ff88eac0","tid":352880,"uid":14012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Pituitary adenoma <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thebraintumourcharity.org/understanding-brain-tumours/living-with-a-brain-tumour/side-effects/depression-and-brain-tumours/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebraintumourcharity.org%2Funderstanding-brain-tumours%2Fliving-with-a-brain-tumour%2Fside-effects%2Fdepression-and-brain-tumours%2F&h=8829e68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長期抑鬱係咪會導致腦瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔肯定<br />\n不過心理醫生叫我拎哂啲report同片 去比佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8b6c772f61d742d600aee9def2d8a56a69570b","tid":352880,"uid":14012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好慘⋯<br />\n個瘤除左有奶水之外對你生活有無影響<br />\n例如頭痛果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭痛 頭暈 發冷 <br />\n成日無啦啦面青口唇白 嚇到我呀媽好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對唔住呀 我唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3058014117743cc2fcc7412e39f81e931212e9c","tid":352880,"uid":14012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抑鬱一年好小事啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過 其實已經兩三年 係以前一路冇睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"